<section id="trust" class="trust">
	<div class="container">
		<h2 class="section-title">信任保證</h2>
		<p class="section-subtitle">讓您購買無憂</p>
		
		<div class="trust-grid">
			<div class="trust-card">
				<div class="trust-icon">📜</div>
				<h3>一物一證</h3>
				<p>每件翡翠原石均附帶專業鑒定證書，保證品質真實</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="trust-card">
				<div class="trust-icon">💰</div>
				<h3>本地匯率</h3>
				<p>匯率走本地匯率，比國際匯率低近50%，價格更優惠</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="trust-card">
				<div class="trust-icon">🛡️</div>
				<h3>源頭直採</h3>
				<p>親赴緬甸礦區直接採購，省去中間環節，品質更有保障</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="trust-card">
				<div class="trust-icon">📊</div>
				<h3>20%代購費</h3>
				<p>收費透明，只賺取20%代購費，不隱藏費用</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="trust-card">
				<div class="trust-icon">🏢</div>
				<h3>瑞麗公司</h3>
				<p>瑞麗設有公司，誠信經營，資質齊全</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="trust-card">
				<div class="trust-icon">🔧</div>
				<h3>合作工廠</h3>
				<p>擁有合作的加工廠，提供一站式服務</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.trust {
		background-color: var(--color-light);
	}
	
	.trust-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
	}
	
	.trust-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-align: center;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}
	
	.trust-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
	}
	
	.trust-card:hover .trust-icon {
		transform: scale(1.15) rotate(5deg);
	}
	
	.trust-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}
	
	.trust-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
	}
	
	.trust-card p {
		color: var(--color-gray);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 992px) {
		.trust-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 576px) {
		.trust-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
